      <section class="content">
        <p>Hi rics, this is the first time na magcoconfess ako sa isang tao na gusto ko and i think eto na rin yung last hahaha. Gusto kita since entrep groupings. I started to like u nung nagsasama na tayo as a group, nung una sobrang naamaze lang ako sa pagiging hard working student mo at the same time pagseserve mo din kay God, and then hindi ko na namalayan na nahulog na pala ako sayo.</p>
        <p>Sobrang cringe ik hahaha ito pala yung feeling maexcite sa taong unexpected kong magugustuhan. l know that you only see me as a friend or maybe just ur blockmate and i’m okay with that, really I am. I never said anything kase ayokong maging awkward or put any pressure on you. I am confessing to let you know about what and how I feel about you, Hindi naman din ako nageexpect ng anything from you, and I respect whatever and whoever na nagpapasaya sayo.</p>
        <p>Being friends is enough, If it’s the only way para mapalapit parin sayo. I'm not taking advantage of anything this is just honestly how i feel. You’ve just been someone I genuinely care about, and gusto ko lang maging honest about that. Also no need to worry, wala naman magbabago satin unless you want them to.</p>
        <p>Anyways, I'm not attending to church just to see u kase ang mindset ko na kabaligtaran ng nakikita ng iba is ikaw yung ginagamit ni Lord sakin para mapalapit ulit ako sakaniya and sobrang thankful din ako sayo dahil don.</p>

